Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哒哒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ta da
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:00:57.74,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(685.333,736.667)}圣诞老人收
Dialogue: 1,0:00:57.74,0:01:00.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这礼物是送给圣诞老人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.74,0:01:00.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This gift is for Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人也得有礼物  对吧小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:03.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Even Santa deserves a gift, right Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa Claus, Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's on his way
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要送他一份礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.75,0:01:10.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm giving him a present
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让他带到雪橇上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That he'll take back on his sleigh
Dialogue: 1,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  我都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, I forgot
Dialogue: 1,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,缩小术
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shrink-o
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:01.85,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(984,1000.667)}圣诞老人收
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,七个月后
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好意思  沙发先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.27,0:02:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mr. Sofa
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看啊  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.49,0:02:16.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at that, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我去年圣诞节留给圣诞老人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the present I left for Santa last Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是很棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.91,0:02:20.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去年圣诞节留给圣诞老人的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:24.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The present I left for Santa last Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他没收到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.75,0:02:27.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He never got it
Dialogue: 1,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这坏事坏得不能再坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:29.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is the worst disaster that's ever happened
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我给圣诞老人的礼物迟到了212天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My present to Santa is 212 days late
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟到了  真是个悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:39.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Late, it's a tragedy
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.51,0:02:46.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我快乐逍遥的世界变得既黑暗又沉闷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:46.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My joyful carefree world is growing dark and dreary
Dialogue: 1,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我活不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't go on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行  要继续活
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:51.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I'll go on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我真活不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:54.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can't go on
Dialogue: 1,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,五星好演技
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:00.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Five stars
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我这不是在演戏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, I wasn't acting
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人没收到圣诞礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:05.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa never got his Christmas present
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那为啥不亲自送给人家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.70,0:03:08.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So why not just deliver it to him?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为啥不亲自送给人家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.00,0:03:12.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why not just deliver it to him?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这想法太扯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's a dumb idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:15.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.55,0:03:16.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great
Dialogue: 1,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是要怎么过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:18.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But how will we get there?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走路走不了那么远
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't walk that far
Dialogue: 1,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱俩可以互相推过去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can push and shove each other
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:26.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great idea
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱一天都不能再迟下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:28.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We can't let it be one more day late
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行了  你先推我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:31.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, me first
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轮我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:36.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My turn
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.40,0:03:41.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.40,0:03:41.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在不是七月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's July?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(658.667,592.667)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天是个当坏人的好日子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a good day to be bad
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.92,0:04:02.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你鼻子上有干鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.92,0:04:02.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a booger
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心  朋友间就该互帮互助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.89,0:04:08.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, that's what friends are for
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.18,0:04:09.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,擤出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.18,0:04:09.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blow
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.10,0:04:13.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:13.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我见过最丑的鼻涕了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:18.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the ugliest booger I've ever seen
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个疯子走路能别老是摔着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can't you screwballs walk without falling?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.03,0:04:28.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要把自己一路推到北极去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:26.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're pushing and shoving ourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.62,0:04:28.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,all the way to the North Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我必须要把礼物给圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to give Santa his Christmas present
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:32.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我恨死那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.33,0:04:33.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hate that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自从我留了这个刺青以来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.66,0:04:35.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's had me on a naughty list
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就一直把我记在淘气名单上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,ever since I got this tattoo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:39.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,848.667)}生来淘气
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是我能打入圣诞老人基地内部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If I can break into Santa's lair
Dialogue: 1,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黑进他的主机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,hack his mainframe
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把我状态从淘气改成善良
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:47.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,change my status from naughty to nice
Dialogue: 1,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就能向他要蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:51.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could ask for the Krabby Patty secret formula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后他就非把它给我不可了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:53.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and he'd have to give it to me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我跟你们一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:55.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm coming with you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来推一把吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:57.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pushed or shoved?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别这么搞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Shrimp that
Dialogue: 1,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要风风光光地过去  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.36,0:05:01.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We are going in style, babies
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.78,0:05:03.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,555.333)}海之霸
Dialogue: 1,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我为了在僵尸末日期间
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.49,0:05:11.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I built it to fly and run over bodies
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,飞天顺便碾压尸体特别打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:13.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,during the zombie apocalypse
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过在雪上行驶也挺管用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it'll work on snow too
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们要从太平洋走到北冰洋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll take the Pacific to the Arctic
Dialogue: 1,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后越过冰雪到达北极
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:22.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,then over ice and snow to the North Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,轻轻松松就能到圣诞老人那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy-peasy, Santa-squeezy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.56,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1306.667,1000.667)}海顶两万里
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:31.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seat belts
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  安全第一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course, safety first
Dialogue: 1,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切就绪  痞老板船长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All secured, Captain Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All secured
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经后悔要跑这一趟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.69,0:05:45.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm already regretting this trip
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:47.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930.667,984.667)}点火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:58.58,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(426.667,518)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We did it
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快看那些小鱼崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at those tiny little fish
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.30,0:06:12.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回位子上坐好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:15.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back to your seats
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全带指示灯没亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The seat belt sign is off
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天外来客来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The visitors, they're here
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他见到我们貌似很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:26.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He seemed happy to see us
Dialogue: 1,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会飞的躺椅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:32.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A flying lawn chair
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿来吧你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.42,0:06:46.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,盒子里面的是个啥东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's in this box anyway?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.38,0:06:50.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a surprise
Dialogue: 1,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望是用来炸那啤酒肚小丑的臭气弹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:55.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope it's a stink bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for that pot-bellied jingle joker
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人才没有啤酒肚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:07:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa is not pot-bellied
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只是患了季节性腹胀罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:02.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He just suffers from seasonal bloating
Dialogue: 1,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行行行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要睡觉去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to sleep
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可这玩意要谁来开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.57,0:07:07.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But who will fly this thing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我设成自动驾驶模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:09.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I put it on automatic pilot
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你跟那个粉红傻蛋可以打地铺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.65,0:07:12.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You and that pink moron can sleep on the floor
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个白痴在搞什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.93,0:07:32.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you imbeciles doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们找到北极了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We found the North Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,北极比你说的要近多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It was way closer than you said
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,北极
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:38.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,North Pole?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Impossible
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我睡多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How long was I asleep?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,地面越来越近感觉好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Funny how the ground keeps getting closer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.48,0:07:53.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1024,814)}圣诞世界主题乐园
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到圣诞世界主题乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Christmas Land Theme Park
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这天天都是圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.49,0:07:53.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where every day is Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,滚出我的位子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get out of my seat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,安全带指示灯亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.75,0:08:04.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The seat belt sign is on
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,机组人员  准备降落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cabin crew, prepare for landing
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真的会降落吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you actually know how to land?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know how to crash land
Dialogue: 1,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的安全带
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:24.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My seat belt
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是北极
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The North Pole
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1293.333,763.333)}北极
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.49,0:08:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We made it
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你们两个脑残搞了什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look what you two broken brain buffoons did
Dialogue: 1,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们彻底把导航弄坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You completely destroyed the navigation system
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别生气嘛  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.38,0:08:56.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be mad, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱都到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:08:57.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看这好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at all this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.14,0:09:05.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1269.333,406)}糖果
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's elves
Dialogue: 1,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的驯鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.74,0:09:15.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's reindeer
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有点不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something's wrong here
Dialogue: 1,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这里居然不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It isn't even cold
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,而且看看这雾霾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:25.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And look at this smog
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既有雪又有雾霾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's snow and smog?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那叫雪霾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.09,0:09:30.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's "snog"
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.09,0:09:38.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's workshop
Dialogue: 1,0:09:38.43,0:09:43.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做玩具  勤工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:43.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Making toys, work, work, work
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的精灵们好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.68,0:09:45.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, Santa's elves
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:47.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.60,0:09:52.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,做  勤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:52.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make, work--
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人已经尽力实现自动化生产了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:56.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like Santa's gone all in for automation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1208,512.667)}见圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.36,0:09:59.37,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1197.334,854.001)}圣诞主题公厕
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家快看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.78,0:09:59.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey guys, look
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面写着  见圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It says, "meet Santa Claus"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.12,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(328,923.333)}见圣诞老人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都快来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, guys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去见圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:08.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's meet Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们总算到了  小礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're finally here, little present
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.97,0:10:17.76,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(922.667,374)}见真正的\N圣诞老人
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不得不说  这地方太假了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.51,0:10:21.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guys, I hate to say this, but this place is a sham
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有种被骗的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know why, but we're being tricked
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板  圣诞节的精髓在于信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:28.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, Plankton, Christmas is about believing
Dialogue: 1,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实  圣诞节的精髓于血样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Christmas is about bleeding, man
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不是亲眼见到连我都不信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't believe it if I didn't see it with my own eye
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那个大胡子奇葩本人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The bearded weirdo in the flesh
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们圣诞节想要什么礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.85,0:11:05.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What would you like for Christmas?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,静一静  孩子们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pipe down, children
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.03,0:11:24.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob SquarePants?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:25.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你知不知道我是你的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did you know that I'm your biggest fan?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真好心  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's very sweet of you Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过其实海盗派斯才是我的头号粉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.21,0:11:34.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but actually Patchy the Pirate is my biggest fan
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们好啊  海绵宝宝派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:38.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ahoy, SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me, Patchy the Pirate
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.76,0:11:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patchy the Pirate?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你居然是圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.43,0:11:48.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're Santa?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  我只是在圣诞乐园扮圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:52.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, I just play Santa here in Christmas Land Theme Park
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我的副业
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's me side-hustle
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就知道这不是北极
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.02,0:11:57.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew this wasn't the North Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,北极
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:11:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,North Pole?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不对  这可是恩斯诺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:01.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, man, this be Encino
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们离北极还有四千英里远
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:04.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're almost 4,000 miles from the North Pole
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要把你们俩都灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna destroy you two
Dialogue: 1,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,四千英里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,4,000 miles?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是GPS没坏就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:15.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If only our GPS wasn't busted
Dialogue: 1,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你们导航
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can help with global positioning
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在GPS发明以前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Way before GPS
Dialogue: 1,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海盗都用这种叫地图的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pirates used these things called maps
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们也会需要用到指南针
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:27.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And you'll need a compass too
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:30.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy holidays
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,死鹦鹉想挨揍是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.61,0:12:38.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Polly want a smacker?
Dialogue: 1,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那谢谢了  派斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks, Patchy
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们该上路去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Guess we'll be on our way
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:46.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Goodbye
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝你们好运
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:46.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good luck
Dialogue: 1,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是见到圣诞老人  就说我要换鹦鹉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If you see Santy Claus, tell him I want a new parrot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要换个新海盗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I want a new pirate
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.04,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(936,662)}恩斯诺
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  我们这是在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(669.333,384.667)}北极
Dialogue: 1,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人工厂  就在前方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:18.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,S-S-Santa's workshop, dead ahead
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,刚好赶到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,J-j-just in time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我快冻死了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm f-f-freezing
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就要到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1592,1022)}北极
Dialogue: 1,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这痞老板冰棍好吃不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.16,0:13:33.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How you doing with that Plankton pop?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我等不及要吃有嚼劲的夹心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.25,0:13:36.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to get to the chewy middle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  痞老板哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey Patrick, where's Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.14,0:13:48.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.14,0:13:48.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃点口香糖吧你  小臭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:57.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Eat a breath mint, trench mouth
Dialogue: 1,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那好吧  我要敲门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.94,0:14:00.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, here it goes
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们样子好好看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:08.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You guys look great
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢你们的宇航头盔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.74,0:14:11.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I like your spaceman helmets
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是还要再过三个月才过万圣节的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But it's not Halloween for another three months
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们不是来过万圣节的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're not here for Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是来找圣诞老人的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.46,0:14:17.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're here for Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我有自己的日程安排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got my own agenda
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以说到这咱就分道扬镳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so this is where we part company
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真对不起  圣诞老人不在的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.96,0:14:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Santa's not home
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他跟太太在阿鲁巴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:29.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's in Aruba with the Missus
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是给你们这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:32.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here you go anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.65,0:14:40.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But--
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,万圣节快乐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:43.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy Halloween
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:06.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's inside
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可真是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jeez
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要把圣诞老人的礼物放他树下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:15.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I have to get Santa's present under his tree
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱必须得进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We've got to get inside
Dialogue: 1,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:19.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm on it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,用圣诞老人的风格进去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:24.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll go in Santa style
Dialogue: 1,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就顺着烟囱走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:25.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Down the chimney
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,行  就用你的办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:30.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine, we'll go with your idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的主机到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now where in Kris Kringle is Santa's mainframe?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有主机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No mainframe
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.50,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1452,256)}圣诞老人工厂
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,just lame brains
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这是想去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:48.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是说我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.51,0:15:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是个小精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:52.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm just a little elf
Dialogue: 1,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你味道一点都不像精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't smell like no elf
Dialogue: 1,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.85,0:15:58.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关你屁事  你个驼鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:00.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's it to you, you moose?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,戴什  当瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:06.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Dasher, Dancer
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.27,0:16:06.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,普兰瑟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:06.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Prancer
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,维克森  科密
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Vixen, Comet
Dialogue: 1,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,丘比特  唐纳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.15,0:16:09.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cupid, Donner
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.11,0:16:09.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,布利岑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.11,0:16:09.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blitzen
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看样子圣诞专车都到齐了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, looks like we got a whole Christmas special here
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.91,0:16:22.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好来玩驯鹿游戏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:22.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready for some reindeer games?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天下太平
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Peace on earth?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们蹄子上的玩意最好是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:31.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That better be mud on your hooves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是这了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:37.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的圣诞树
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's Christmas tree
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们在那
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.52,0:16:49.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There they are
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是那些来要糖的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:51.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the trick-or-treaters
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩具贼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:53.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toy thieves
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:55.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Christmas crooks
Dialogue: 1,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抓住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:56.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get 'em
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  要怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:59.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, what do we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:00.20,0:17:00.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬树
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.20,0:17:00.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Climb
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们要上树了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're going up the tree
Dialogue: 1,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别让他们跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:05.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't let 'em get away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:10.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1626.667,374)}圣诞老人工厂
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警报响了  都去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:09.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We better check that alarm
Dialogue: 1,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,被我弄累了是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wore you down, didn't I?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这堆呆头傻鹿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:20.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You meat head cari-boobs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,玩具贼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toy thieves
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Elves
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.27,0:17:31.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the Father Christmas is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们都已经控制住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got this under control
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回你们的鹿厩去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go back to your stables
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太过分了  精灵小弟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not cool elf bros
Dialogue: 1,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一点都不好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:17:59.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not funny
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:14.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我似乎把充满不满情绪的种子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.28,0:18:17.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It looks like I have sowed the seeds of discontent
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,播撒在圣诞老人的屋子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the house of Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拐杖糖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:23.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Candy cane
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人的主机
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa's mainframe
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:43.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I found it
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(976,232.667)}善良名单添加
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:45.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1538.667,750)}保存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:44.06,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(501.334,740)\clip(405.333,666.667,477.333,741.333)}痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.06,0:18:44.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(501.334,740)\clip(408,661.333,533.333,741.333)}痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.14,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(501.334,740)}痞老板
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,得亏有那两个白痴转移注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:50.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks to those two idiots causing a distraction
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:51.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I did it
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我名字已经写进善良名单上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.11,0:18:54.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name is the nice list
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只要再连当几个月大善人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:57.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I just gotta be good for the next few months
Dialogue: 1,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有什么难的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.99,0:18:59.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How hard could that be?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这都怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What the ho, ho, ho is going on here?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在加勒比海跟太太正舒服着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:10.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was kicking back with the Missus in the Caribbean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,突然我的静音警报就响了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.92,0:19:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,when my silent alarm went off
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should've known
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是个麻烦精
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're a menace
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只想把你去年圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All I wanted to do was leave you this present
Dialogue: 1,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没收到的礼物给你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that you didn't get last Christmas
Dialogue: 1,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,迟到了213天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.44,0:19:35.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,213 days late
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.48,0:19:36.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,礼物永远都不嫌迟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A present is never too late
Dialogue: 1,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你真是好心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.03,0:19:40.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How sweet
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,精灵跟驯鹿都没送过我礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:43.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not even the elves or reindeer get me presents
Dialogue: 1,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:47.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,应该现在就打开吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Should I open it now?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这份礼物独一无二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.92,0:19:58.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's one of a kind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:00.22,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(394.667,848.667)}胶水
Dialogue: 1,0:20:01.38,0:20:04.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹黄堡的秘密配方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:04.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krabby Patty secret formula?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要把它送给圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's giving it to Santa Claus
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还改什么名单  秘方就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:10.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the list, the formula's right here
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上就能到我手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could have it now
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.82,0:20:23.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Plankton?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又在干淘气事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're being naughty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.99,0:20:29.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞老人  我生来淘气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:29.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Santa, I was born to be naughty
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.49,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1176,840.667)}生来淘气
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.43,0:20:33.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是还给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.01,0:20:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you can have this back
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:42.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My bad
Dialogue: 1,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, good--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是我好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.18,0:20:45.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很善良  一点都不淘气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:47.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm being nice, not naughty
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.47,0:20:49.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你念出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:49.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, read it out loud
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.02,0:20:51.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点  念出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:53.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go on, read it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,念出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Read it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,亲爱的圣诞老人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:20:59.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Dear Santa
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,世界上没有一份礼物能够大到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:02.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"there isn't a present big enough
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能够足以表达你把多少欢乐带给了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"to express how much joy you've brought
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.20,0:21:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全世界的小朋友和海底生物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"to all the children and sea creatures of the world
Dialogue: 1,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因此这其实只是份简单的感谢信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"So this is just a simple thank you note
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.79,0:21:11.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.83,0:21:15.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爱你的  你的朋友海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:15.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Signed, with love, your pal SpongeBob"
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,上面有错别字
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got a typo here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.63,0:21:22.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How touching
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是太美好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is beautiful
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢你  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:27.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没痞老板帮忙我也没法顺利抵达的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:28.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have made it here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,without the help of Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他其实也没那么淘气的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.47,0:21:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's really not that naughty
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然也少不了好朋友派大星的帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:34.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And of course, my best friend Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝我圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:39.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy holidays to me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.77,0:21:41.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,第二年圣诞节
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.86,0:21:43.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(525.333,566)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,祝大家圣诞快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:47.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy holidays, everybody
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢尔顿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:49.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sheldon
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,煤块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:51.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lump of coal
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肯定又是煤块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.21,0:21:57.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another lump of coal no doubt
Dialogue: 1,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.42,0:22:00.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's this?
